      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>The collection consists of material of a homoerotic nature assembled by Gordon Martin, and includes
         typescripts and photocopies of erotic/pornographic short prose fictions, a few of which are illustrated
         with drawings or photographs; catalogs and brochures of mail order enterprises dealing in erotica and
         pornography; and erotic and pornographic films.</p>
      </scopecontent>
